{"lemma":"حَرَسَةٍ","slug":"حَرَسَةٍ","root":"ح.ر.س","root_slug":"ح-ر-س","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ر-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7625"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"guard, watchman, guardian, keeper"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"defender"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"governor"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"short for حَارِس مَرْمًى (ḥāris marman, “goalkeeper”)","tags":["abbreviation","alt-of"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"guarding, keeping, preserving"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"vigilant"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb حَرَسَ (ḥarasa, “to guard”)."},"ipa":["/ħaː.ris/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7625","headword_ar":"حَرَسَهُ","root":"Hrs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiraAsapN","text_ar":"حِرَاسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarosN","text_ar":"حَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓ the former is a simple subst., (Msb,) and the latter is an inf. n. only on the authority of analogy, though often used by [the Hanafee Imám] Mohammad, (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He guarded, kept, preserved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took care of, him"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb:) [and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HArshu","text_ar":"حارسهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he guarded him, being guarded by him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 3 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rbA^","text_ar":"ربا"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harasahu A@ll~`hu mina AlbalaA='i","text_ar":"حَرَسَهُ ا@للّٰهُ مِنَ البَلَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God guard him from trial,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affliction"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adaAma HiraAsatahu","text_ar":"اَدَامَ حِرَاسَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May He continue the guarding of him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harasa","text_ar":"حَرَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarosN","text_ar":"حَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stole;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K;) [ironically used in this sense; see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaArisN","text_ar":"حَارِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtrs","text_ar":"احترس","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he stole"},{"kind":"text","text":"a sheep or goat"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or both,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he stole"},{"kind":"text","text":"camels and sheep or goats"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by night, and ate"},{"kind":"text","text":"them: (TA:) or the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he stole"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a sheep or the like]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Fárábee, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the place of pasturage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarasaniY $aApF","text_ar":"حَرَسَنِى شَاةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Mgh,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHorasaniY","text_ar":"اَحْرَسَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) [but the latter is perhaps a mistranscription for ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotarasaniY","text_ar":"اِحْتَرَسَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stole from me a sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","Sh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}